Sentencas: Ni cermet anodes were prepared from nanoparticle solid solutions of V2O3-CeO2-ZrO2 with various CeO2 contents, (Y2O3)(0.08)(CeO2)(x)(ZrO2)(0.92-x) (x = 0-0.08).
Titulo: Ni cermet solid oxide fuel cell anodes prepared from nanoparticle Y2O3-CeO2-ZrO2 solid solutions

Sentencas: The performance of cells with anodes prepared from solid solutions was better than that of the cells with anodes prepared by physical mixing.
Titulo: Ni cermet solid oxide fuel cell anodes prepared from nanoparticle Y2O3-CeO2-ZrO2 solid solutions

Sentencas: The performance of cells with anodes prepared from solid solutions increased with an increase in CeO2 content.
Titulo: Ni cermet solid oxide fuel cell anodes prepared from nanoparticle Y2O3-CeO2-ZrO2 solid solutions

Sentencas: Results of impedance analysis of the anode suggested that conduction of O2- is enhanced by CeO2 particles.
Titulo: Ni cermet solid oxide fuel cell anodes prepared from nanoparticle Y2O3-CeO2-ZrO2 solid solutions

Sentencas: The rate of coke deposition decreased with an increase in CeO2 content of the solid solution.
Titulo: Ni cermet solid oxide fuel cell anodes prepared from nanoparticle Y2O3-CeO2-ZrO2 solid solutions

Sentencas: The rate of C removal increased with an increase in conduction of O2-, suggesting that C reacted with O2- ions of CeO2 particles for steam reforming of methane.
Titulo: Ni cermet solid oxide fuel cell anodes prepared from nanoparticle Y2O3-CeO2-ZrO2 solid solutions
